### 健康检查
GET http://localhost:8080/api/health


#### 功能列表
GET http://localhost:8080/api/analysis/list


#### 获取分析器参数说明
GET http://localhost:8080/api/analysis/params/短期急涨


#### 合约列表
GET http://localhost:8080/api/analysis/symbols


#### 刷新合约列表
POST http://localhost:8080/api/analysis/symbols/refresh



#### 查看所有最新结果
GET http://localhost:8080/api/analysis/latest


#### 查看指定分析器最新结果
GET http://localhost:8080/api/analysis/latest/短期急涨


# ============================================================
# 同步执行 —— 连续上涨
# 参数: days=int(默认3)
# ============================================================

#### 连续上涨 — 默认参数
POST http://localhost:8080/api/analysis/sync/连续上涨


#### 连续上涨 — 自定义days
POST http://localhost:8080/api/analysis/sync/连续上涨
Content-Type: application/json

{"days": 3}

#### 连续上涨 — Query参数
POST http://localhost:8080/api/analysis/sync/连续上涨?days=5


# ============================================================
# 同步执行 —— 连涨今跌
# 参数: days=int(默认3)
# ============================================================

#### 连涨今跌 — 默认参数
POST http://localhost:8080/api/analysis/sync/连涨今跌


#### 连涨今跌 — 自定义days
POST http://localhost:8080/api/analysis/sync/连涨今跌
Content-Type: application/json

{"days": 4}

#### 连涨今跌 — Query参数
POST http://localhost:8080/api/analysis/sync/连涨今跌?days=5


# ============================================================
# 同步执行 —— 大幅上涨
# 参数: days=int(默认7), thresholdPercent=double(默认50)
# ============================================================

#### 大幅上涨 — 默认参数
POST http://localhost:8080/api/analysis/sync/大幅上涨


#### 大幅上涨 — 自定义
POST http://localhost:8080/api/analysis/sync/大幅上涨
Content-Type: application/json

{"days": 30, "thresholdPercent": 100}

#### 大幅上涨 — Query参数
POST http://localhost:8080/api/analysis/sync/大幅上涨?days=14&thresholdPercent=80


# ============================================================
# 同步执行 —— 连跌今涨
# 参数: days=int(默认5)
# ============================================================

#### 连跌今涨 — 默认参数
POST http://localhost:8080/api/analysis/sync/连跌今涨


#### 连跌今涨 — 自定义days
POST http://localhost:8080/api/analysis/sync/连跌今涨
Content-Type: application/json

{"days": 3}

#### 连跌今涨 — Query参数
POST http://localhost:8080/api/analysis/sync/连跌今涨?days=3


# ============================================================
# 同步执行 —— 缓涨币
# 参数: days=int(默认7), maxDailyChangePercent=double(默认3)
# ============================================================

#### 缓涨币 — 默认参数
POST http://localhost:8080/api/analysis/sync/缓涨币


#### 缓涨币 — 自定义
POST http://localhost:8080/api/analysis/sync/缓涨币
Content-Type: application/json

{"days": 7, "maxDailyChangePercent": 5}

#### 缓涨币 — Query参数
POST http://localhost:8080/api/analysis/sync/缓涨币?days=7&maxDailyChangePercent=2


# ============================================================
# 同步执行 —— 价涨仓增
# 参数: days=int(默认5), maxPriceRisePercent=double(默认10), minOiRisePercent=double(默认20)
# ============================================================

#### 价涨仓增 — 默认参数
POST http://localhost:8080/api/analysis/sync/价涨仓增


#### 价涨仓增 — 自定义(涨幅≤15%、持仓增长≥30%)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/analysis/sync/价涨仓增
Content-Type: application/json

{"days": 5, "maxPriceRisePercent": 15, "minOiRisePercent": 80}

#### 价涨仓增 — 自定义(短线)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/analysis/sync/价涨仓增
Content-Type: application/json

{"days": 2, "maxPriceRisePercent": 10, "minOiRisePercent": 20}

#### 价涨仓增 — Query参数
POST http://localhost:8080/api/analysis/sync/价涨仓增?days=3&maxPriceRisePercent=5&minOiRisePercent=10


# ============================================================
# 同步执行 —— 低位插针
# 参数: days=int(默认7), maxPriceChangePercent=double(默认10), lowPricePercentile=double(默认30)
# ============================================================

#### 低位插针 — 默认参数
POST http://localhost:8080/api/analysis/sync/低位插针


#### 低位插针 — 自定义(放宽价格波动、低位分位线5%)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/analysis/sync/低位插针
Content-Type: application/json

{"days": 15, "maxPriceChangePercent": 20, "lowPricePercentile": 5}

#### 低位插针 — 自定义(长周期)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/analysis/sync/低位插针
Content-Type: application/json

{"days": 30, "maxPriceChangePercent": 15, "lowPricePercentile": 40}

#### 低位插针 — Query参数
POST http://localhost:8080/api/analysis/sync/低位插针?days=7&maxPriceChangePercent=8&lowPricePercentile=20


# ============================================================
# 同步执行 —— 短期急涨 (6因子P/V/B/D/C/T + 起爆加分 0-170)
# 参数: interval=string(默认5m), period=int(默认6), thresholdPercent=double(默认3), minScore=int(默认70)
#       launchBodyRatio=double(默认0.6), launchClosePos=double(默认0.8), launchVolRatio=double(默认3.0), takerBuyRatio=double(默认0.55)
# ============================================================

#### 短期急涨 — 默认参数(5m K线, 6根, ≥3%, ≥70分)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/analysis/sync/短期急涨


#### 短期急涨 — 超短线(1m K线, 低门槛)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/analysis/sync/短期急涨
Content-Type: application/json

{"interval": "1m", "period": 10, "thresholdPercent": 2, "minScore": 50, "launchBodyRatio": 0.5, "takerBuyRatio": 0.5}

#### 短期急涨 — 15m中短线(严格)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/analysis/sync/短期急涨
Content-Type: application/json

{"interval": "15m", "period": 4, "thresholdPercent": 5, "minScore": 80}

#### 短期急涨 — Query参数
POST http://localhost:8080/api/analysis/sync/短期急涨?interval=5m&period=6&thresholdPercent=3&minScore=70


# ============================================================
# 同步执行 —— 底部吸筹 (5因子C/Q/W/O/S评分 0-125)
# 参数: days=int(默认7), minScore=int(默认65), priceChangeMin=double(默认-3), priceChangeMax=double(默认8)
# ============================================================

#### 底部吸筹 — 默认参数
POST http://localhost:8080/api/analysis/sync/底部吸筹


#### 底部吸筹 — 14天周期
POST http://localhost:8080/api/analysis/sync/底部吸筹
Content-Type: application/json

{"days": 14, "minScore": 70, "priceChangeMin": -5, "priceChangeMax": 10}

#### 底部吸筹 — 短线3天
POST http://localhost:8080/api/analysis/sync/底部吸筹
Content-Type: application/json

{"days": 3, "minScore": 55, "priceChangeMin": -2, "priceChangeMax": 5}

#### 底部吸筹 — Query参数
POST http://localhost:8080/api/analysis/sync/底部吸筹?days=10&minScore=50



#### 连续几天持仓量上涨的B
POST http://localhost:8080/api/analysis/sync/持仓量连增
Content-Type: application/json

{"days": 5, "maxPriceRisePercent": 5}


#### 首阴日
POST http://localhost:8080/api/analysis/sync/首阴日
Content-Type: application/json

{"days": 6, "minTotalRisePercent": 40}


# ============================================================
# 同步执行 —— N日高低点
# 参数: days=int(默认7)
# ============================================================

#### N日高低点 — 默认参数
POST http://localhost:8080/api/analysis/sync/N日高低点


#### N日高低点 — 自定义天数
POST http://localhost:8080/api/analysis/sync/N日高低点
Content-Type: application/json

{"days": 14}

#### N日高低点 — Query参数
POST http://localhost:8080/api/analysis/sync/N日高低点?days=3


# ============================================================
# 同步执行 —— N日最低
# 参数: days=int(默认7)
# 只返回 symbol 和最低价
# ============================================================

#### N日最低 — 默认参数
POST http://localhost:8080/api/analysis/sync/N日最低


#### N日最低 — 自定义天数
POST http://localhost:8080/api/analysis/sync/N日最低
Content-Type: application/json

{"days": 30}

#### N日最低 — Query参数
POST http://localhost:8080/api/analysis/sync/N日最低?days=3